programme.desc: Dos Boat meets up with Oliver Ngy and Kevin Harlander in North Central Wisconsin. Oliver and Kevin are here for two things: big musky and delicious panfish. programme.title: Das Boat

programme.desc: In the Das Boat Season 2 finale, Danielle Prewett and fishing guide Frank Smethurst explore Red Lake, MN, targeting freshwater drum, a fish locals dismiss as a nuisance.
